@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Obtener todas las calificaciones
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/grades

###

### Obtener calificacion por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/grades/1

###

### Crear calificacion
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/grades
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "enrollment_id": 1,
  "course_id": 1,
  "period": "P1",
  "score": 8.5,
  "comments": "Buen desempeno",
  "status": "published"
}

###

### Actualizar calificacion
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/grades/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "score": 9.0,
  "comments": "Excelente desempeno",
  "status": "published"
}

###

### Eliminar calificacion fisicamente
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/grades/1

###

### Eliminar calificacion logicamente
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/grades/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "draft"
}
